\id TIT - Ndwewe Bible Version
\h Titus
\toc1 Lihamba lya Paulo kwa Titusi
\toc2 Titus
\toc3 Tit
\mt2 Lihamba lya Paulo kwa
\mt1 Titus
\imt1 Ulongolelo
\ip Lihamba ali kwa Titusi ndo limoo mu mahamba ncheche ghaatyekitwe na Paulo kughenda kwa mundu ghwa kighweka na chepa kwa ngwemko ya bhandu bha Chapanga bhaanhyubhalia Kilisito. Mahamba ghangi mandatu ndo 1 Timoti, na 2 Timoti na Filimoni. Paulo kakintyekela Titusi peni kangi kakityeka handa kukita lisomwe pa kindangabhanji. Tungumanya habhu kiyaha Paulo kangulubhulila umanyi ghwake katwihilika na kangunoghwa kubhegha Nndumila, nnando ghwene Titusi kakimanyagha ubhwabhu abhu. Yingukitilwa kukita Paulo kakityeka lihamba ali nkati ya ngungwa 63-65 mbole ya kubhelekwa Kilisito.
\ip Paulo kangunlaghila Titusi kulilongoha ngwemuko liibheghite mu kigunguli kya Kelete. Paulo kakityeka lihamba ali kwa nningo ghwa kunlaghila Titusi ya kya kuhaghula na kubhahunda hilongohi bha ngwemuko. Paulo kakikamuha malaghilo ghaalandanite na agho mu lihamba lyakantyekelite Timoteo. Lihamba lyake lingulubhulila kya bhuli hilongohi bha ngwemuko bhangunoghwa kuhokamilwa muno. Ngwemuko na hilongohi bhake bha manjubha gha lelo bhangunoghwa kulolekeha milando ayi yinakupalwa kwa hilongohi bha ngwemuko.
\iot Ghaabheghite
\io1 Paulo kangunlaghila Titusi kubhahaghula hilongohi bhaannyitikila Chapanga 1:1-16.
\io1 Kangi kangunlaghila kuahunda bhandu ngati bhalame kya kuntundamila Chapanga 2:1—3:11.
\io1 Muuhiko Paulo kanguyomola lihamba lyake kwa kutyeka malagho gha kuyomolela 3:12-15.
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 Lihamba ali linguhuma kwa nenga Paulo, nndumila ghwa Chapanga na nhundwa ghwa Yesu Kilisito.
\p Nenga nikihaghulighwa kutengelekeha kuhyubhalila Kilisito kwa bhandu bhaahaghulitwe na Chapanga na kualongoha ngati bhatame ulami ghwa kunnogheha Chapanga,
\v 2 ghwene kitamiko kyake ndo udumbilo ghwa kumokola ulami ghwa manjubha ghoha. Chapanga ywanga kulongela uhwangi kakitulagha ulami aghwo pakali na kubhumbwa kwa nnima,
\v 3 naywo kwa nndaluko ghuunoghite kakighuhwimula mu lilagho lyake. Nenga hyubhalika mu lilagho alyo nililandamihe kulandana na ngwiliho ya Chapanga Nlopohi ghwetu.
\p 
\v 4 Nungukutyekela ghwenga Titusi, mwana ghwangu ghwa hoto mu uhyubhalilo ghutulilungite twabhoha.
\p Nungukuyupila umaha na uhihimilo kuhuma kwa Tate Chapanga na kuhuma kwa Kilisito Yesu Nlopohi ghwetu.
\s1 Lihengo lya Titusi akwo Kilete
\p 
\v 5 Hino, nenga nikikuleka kula ku Kilete ngati ghuyitende milando yila yiibheghite yikali kutwihilika, na kuahaghula Aghohi bha ngwemuko ya bhandu bhaabhyubhalilite Kilisito mu kila kigunguli. Ghughakulungwe malaghilo gha nenga,
\v 6 nghohi ghwa ngwemuko ya bhandu bhaabhyubhalilite Kilisito kangunoghwa kabhe mundu ywa nga kubhayilwa, ywakabheghite na nhumbu yumu ghweka, na bhana bhaki anoghelwe bhubho bhabhe bhangunhyubhalila Kilisito, na bhakotoke kumanyikwa mubhulwa ebu ngakatala.
\v 7 Kya bhula kilongohi ghwa ngwemuko ya bhandu bhaabhyubhalila Kilisito ndo nkulu mu lihengo lya Chapanga, kangunoghwa kabheghe mundu ywa nga kubhayilwa. Kakotoke kubheghe mundu yunakulidumba, nnyeyehu ghwa kuyaghabhala, nlobhi, ntenda bhulwa ebu yuna tama ya kumokola mbiya kwa njila ya nga kunoghela.
\v 8 Kanoghwa kabheghe ntekulo na ywakapala milando ya maha. Kanoghwa kabheghe mundu yunakuyukuta, nng'ololeho, ghwa kya Chapanga na yunauhokamo.
\v 9 Kangunnoghwa kakamulile telatela lilagho lya uhyubhalilo handa palihunditwe. Pakahotola kubhayonjokeha myoyo bhangi kwa mahundo ghanakunoghwa na kughahwimula mahokelo gha bhandu bhanakupingikiha mahundo agho.
\p 
\v 10 Kiyaha bhabhegha bhandu atangalo bhangayitikila, bhaabheghite na malagho gha ubhughabhugha nalumu ndo bhala bhamukimati kya ulumula unyagho.
\v 11 Yinogha mbaka kuahibha milomo, kiyaha bhanguyitindingana lubhagha lwoha lwa bhandu kwa kuhunda milando yibhanoghite ng'obhe kuhunda. Bhangutenda habhu ngati bhalimokolele ngalabha kwa ukubhuhi.
\v 12 Hata yumoo ywa ambuye ghwabhe, naywo bhubho ndo Nkelete, kakilongela, “Akaakelete ahwangi manjubha ghoha, ndo handa anyama ahakata, alyegha kwapukwapu na atotoho!”
\v 13 Naywo kakilongela hoto, na kya habhu, ghungunoghwa kubhalakalila kwa ulakalo, ngati bhabhe na bhanakunhyubhalila Kilisito ghwa telatela,
\v 14 bhakotoke kughendelela kukamulila nga hitohe ghweka hya Akaayahudi na malaghilo gha bhala bhandu bhaayilemite hoto.
\v 15 Hilibhi hyoha hibhegha nyanyi kwa bhandu bhayitikilitwe muulongolo ghwa Chapanga, peni kahone kilibhi kiiyitikilitwe kwa bhala bhaahwachila uhokelo na bhanga kuhyubhalila, kiyaha hwacho na malango ghabhe ghahokela.
\v 16 Bhandu handa abha bhangulikwina kukita bhangunmanya Chapanga, peni kwa mandendelo ghabhe bhangunkiluka. Ndo bhandu bha kuyaghabhiha muno na bhangayitika, bhangunoghwa ng'obhe kwa nnando ghwohele ghwa maha.
\c 2
\s1 Mahundo gha hoto
\p 
\v 1 Peni kwa nhalo ghwa ghwenga Titusi, yingukunoghwa kuhunda kulandana na mahundo gha hoto.
\v 2 Ghubhaghombele aghohi alume, kukita yinguanogha kubhegha na ntengeleho, na kutenda mihalo yinakuyegha uhokamo, kangi bhangunogha kubhegha bhanakulilongoha bhene, bhanauhyubhalilo ghwa mahundo gha hoto, upalo na alimbilila.
\v 3 Ubhwabhuabhu ghubhaghombele adala aghohi kukita bhangunoghwa abheghe handa bhaahaghultwe kwa kya Chapanga. Akotoke kubhegha akolekeha ebu alobhi, ngati bhahunde ghala ghaabheghite gha maha,
\v 4 ngati abhatengelekehe ahumbu kabhali kuapala angwana bhabhe na bhana bhabhe,
\v 5 bhahotole kulilongoha bhene, bhaayitikilitwe muulongolo ghwa Chapanga, bhalolekehe maha milando ya ukaya kwabhe, bhabheghe na umaha na bhabhayitikile alume bhabhe, ngati mundu ywoheli kakotoke kuliyuyuha lilagho lya Chapanga.
\p 
\v 6 Ubhwabhuabhu, ghubhabhinilile ahongolo ahotole kulilongoha bhene.
\v 7 Mu milando yoha ghwenga ghungunoghwa ghubheghe nhwano mung'endelo ya maha. Mu mahundo ghako ghubhonehe kukita ghubhegha na mwoyo nyanyi na nng'ololeho.
\v 8 Ghukambuke malagho ghanogha gha nga kukanilwa ngati amyanja bhako bhabhone honi, na bhakotoke kubhegha na kihakata kyohele kyakulongela kwa kya twenga.
\p 
\v 9 Ghubhahunde abhandwa kubhayitikila angwana bhabhe na bhabhayelehe mu milando yoha. Bhakotoke kulimbana nabho,
\v 10 ebu bhakoteke kuayibhila hilibhi hyabhe, kihyengo kyaki bhangunoghwa abhonekane bha maha na ayitikila mu manjubha ghoha, ngati kwa mandendelo ghabhonehe lutiko lwa maha kwa mahundo gha Chapanga.
\p 
\v 11 Kiyaha umaha ghwa Chapanga ghuhwimulighwa ngati kualopoha bhandu bhoha.
\v 12 Umaha aghwo ghungutuhunda kulekana na ng'endelo yohele yiinogha ng'obhe Chapanga, na tama ya nnima, ngati tuhotole kulama kwa kulilongoha twabhene, na tutame kwa ghughololelo na ghana kunnogheha Chapanga munnima aghu,
\v 13 patulindila udumbilo ghwa unonelo, pala paghupala kubwitukila ukulu ghwa Chapanga ghwetu Nkulu na Nlopohi ghwetu Yesu Kilisito.
\v 14 Ywombe kakilibhuha mwene kahweghe kwa kya twenga ngati katukombole kubhuka mu uhokelo ghwoha na kutuyoha tubhe nyanyi bhandu bhake mwene Chapanga, kukita tubhe bhandu bhanakutenda lihengo lya maha.
\p 
\v 15 Hino ghwenga ghuhunde milando ayi yoha, paghuayonjokeha mwoyo na kubhakinya kwa makakala ghako ghoha. Mundu ywoheli kakotoke kukuyuyuha.
\c 3
\s1 Bhula yinguanogha kutama bhala bhaanhyubhalila Kilisito
\p 
\v 1 Ghubhatende bhandu bhakulungwe kukita bhangunoghwa abhatekule atabhala na bhaabheghiti na makakala, bhabhayitikile na bhabhe kala kutenda milando ya maha yoha.
\v 2 Ghubhaghombele bhakotoke kunligha mundu ywohele, ngati bhakotoke kulimbana, na abheghe nuu, na paakibhoneha utetebhalo kwa bhandu bhoha mumanjubha ghoha.
\v 3 Kiyaha manjubha ghamu twenga tukibhegha abhughabhugha, angakatala na ahokelo. Tukibhegha abhandwa bha tama na kubejula ghweka. Tukitama muubhumi ghwa uhokelo na malili, bhandu bhakitukalila na twenga tukibhakalalila.
\v 4 Peni paghuhwimulitwe umaha na upalo ghwake Chapanga na Nlopohi ghwetu,
\v 5 kakitulopoha, na kakitenda habho chepa kwa nnando ghwohele ghwa maha ghutuutendite ngati kwa luhungu lwake, kwa njila ya Nhuki ghwa Chapanga ywakatunemelite kwa kutuyoha ngati tubhelekwe uhyono na tubheghe na ulami ghwa hyono.
\v 6 Chapanga kakitupegha Nhuki ghwake kwa utekulo kwa kukindila Yesu Kilisito, Nlopohi ghwetu,
\v 7 ngati kwa umaha ghwake tumokole kuyitikilwa na tunoghwe kuhala ubhumi ghwa manjubha ghoha ghutughuudumbila.
\v 8 Ali ndo lilagho lya kuhyubhalila.
\p Nungupala ghubhahunde kwa kubhinilila milando ayi, ngati bhala bhaanhyubhalila Chapanga bhahotole kubhegha na kilyakalyaka kya kutenda gha maha. Milando ayi ndo ya maha kangi yibhegha na utopelo kwa bhandu bhoha.
\v 9 Peni ghuhepetuke na malimbano ya kihila mahala, maghombano gha kya lukolo, bhulwa na malimbano gha kya malaghilo. Milando ayi yibhegha ng'obhe na fwambulo na yibhegha ng'obhe na utopelo ghwohele.
\v 10 Mundu ywakayambuha nng'abhaniko ghunkinye pakatandila, na ghunkinye paubhili na handa kaayihwa ng'obhe, ghulekani naywo.
\v 11 Kiyaha ghungumanya kukita mundu handa aywo kahobha na ulemwa ghwake ghungubhoneha kukita kalitosa mwene.
\s1 Malagho gha uhiko
\p 
\v 12 Kamu panunnaghila Alitema ebu Tikiko kwa ghwenga, ghulopokele kuhika kunnola akwo Nikopoli, kiyaha namula kutama akwo mu manjubha gha nndaluko ghwa kipepo.
\v 13 Ghukakalike kuntangatila nsomi ghwa malaghilo Zenasi na Apolo, ngati ahotole kuyanda mwanja ghwabhe, na ghulyaghile akotoke kupelelwa kubhegha na kilibhi kyoheli kyabhakipalite.
\v 14 Bhandu bhetu nabho bhalihunde kutenda gha maha, ngati bhabhatangatile bhaabheghite na upalo ghwa hilibhi hyaahipala ngati akotoke kutama ubhumi ghwa nga kutangatila.
\p 
\v 15 Bhandu bhoha bhaabheghite papamu na nenga bhangughujambuha. Ghubhajambuhe bhala bhoha bhaatupala.
\p Nungubhayupila mabhoha umaha ghwa Chapanga.
